<p>作者<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/swanknight" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3342448); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3342448&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606816389" alt="SwanKnight" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3342448)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/swanknight" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3342448); return false;">SwanKnight</a></span></p>
