<p><span style="font-size:130%;"><strong>蒸发</strong></span></p>
<p>作者<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/star-lyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5096130); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5096130&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606816389" alt="Star Lyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5096130)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/star-lyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5096130); return false;">Star Lyn</a></span></p>
