<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="font-size:130%;"><strong>“嘟——，嘟——”</strong></span></p>
<p>作者<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agent-phage" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2950095); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2950095&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606816389" alt="Agent Phage" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2950095)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/agent-phage" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2950095); return false;">Agent Phage</a></span></p>
